              <module name="Search" layoutPanel="panel_row5_col1">
                <param name="search"><![CDATA[
`custom_index` ( sourcetype="cube_cdr" OR sourcetype="cube_cdr_compact ")
``` inline version of the Cisco CDR apps get_concurrency macro, the complex version with a split-by ```

| eval increment = if(duration>0,mvappend("1","-1"),"0")
| mvexpand type
| mvexpand increment
| eval _time = if(increment==1, _time, _time + duration)
| sort 0 + _time
| fillnull type value="NULL"
| streamstats sum(increment) as post_concurrency by type
| eval concurrency = if(increment==-1, post_concurrency+1, post_concurrency)
``` inline version of the Cisco CDR apps timechart_for_concurrency macro, the complex version with split-by and bins```
| timechart fixedrange=false bins=400 max(concurrency) as max_concurrency last(post_concurrency) as last_concurrency by type limit=60
| filldown last_concurrency*
| foreach "max_concurrency:*" [eval <<MATCHSTR>>=coalesce('max_concurrency:<<MATCHSTR>>','last_concurrency:<<MATCHSTR>>')]
| fields - last_concurrency* max_concurrency*
| fillnull
                ]]></param>
                <module name="HTML">
                  <param name="html"><![CDATA[
                    <h3>Max Concurrent calls/meetings</h3>
                  ]]></param>
                </module>

